&lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://johannesodland.github.io/2024/12/12/web-wish-12-custom-css-functions.html"&gt;https://johannesodland.github.io/2024/12/12/web-wish-12-custom-css-functions.html&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
