Appeared as a missing feature in State of CSS 2024 &lt;&lt;a rel="nofollow" href="https://2024.stateofcss.com/en-US/usage/#css_missing_features"&gt;https://2024.stateofcss.com/en-US/usage/#css_missing_features&lt;/a&gt;&gt;.
