&gt;&gt; for prefetch:  Fetch Standard 
&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#:~:text=If%20httpRequest%E2%80%99s%20initiator%20is%20%22prefetch%22%2C%20then%20set%20a%20structured%20field%20value%20given%20"&gt;https://fetch.spec.whatwg.org/#:~:text=If%20httpRequest%E2%80%99s%20initiator%20is%20%22prefetch%22%2C%20then%20set%20a%20structured%20field%20value%20given%20&lt;/a&gt;(%60Sec%2DPurpose%60%2C%20the%20token%20prefetch)%20in%20httpRequest%E2%80%99s%20header%20list&gt;
