&lt;pre&gt;Enterprises tend not to run beta-channel. They also tend to turn off
metrics and crash reporting. A slow rollout as Alex is suggesting will
hopefully catch issues early but we also need to be ready to react to
urgent regressions as this reaches 100% on stable-channel.
