&lt;span class="subject"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=subject:%22Re%5C%3A+%5C%5BEXTERNAL%5C%5D+Re%5C%3A+%5C%5Bblink%5C-dev%5C%5D+Intent+to+Ship%5C%3A+Fire+error+event+instead+of+throwing+for+CSP+blocked+worker%22&amp;o=newest" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;Re: [EXTERNAL] Re: [blink-dev] Intent to Ship: Fire error event instead of throwing for CSP blocked worker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
