&lt;span class="subject"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=subject:%22Re%5C%3A+%5C%5Bblink%5C-dev%5C%5D+Re%5C%3A+Intent+to+Ship%5C%3A+H26x+Codec+support+updates+for+MediaRecorder%22&amp;o=newest" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span itemprop="name"&gt;Re: [blink-dev] Re: Intent to Ship: H26x Codec support updates for MediaRecorder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
