&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; I've added a few so far--WPT coverage for the Web Speech API in general
&gt;&gt; is pretty basic at the moment. I'm planning on adding more
&gt;&gt; comprehensive coverage. Here are the ones relevant to this proposal:
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/web_tests/external/wpt/speech-api/SpeechRecognition-installOnDeviceSpeechRecognitiRecognition.https.html"&gt;https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/web_tests/external/wpt/speech-api/SpeechRecognition-installOnDeviceSpeechRecognitiRecognition.https.html&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/web_tests/external/wpt/speech-api/SpeechRecognition-installOnDeviceSpeechRecognition.https.html"&gt;https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:third_party/blink/web_tests/external/wpt/speech-api/SpeechRecognition-installOnDeviceSpeechRecognition.https.html&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
