&lt;pre&gt;Sorry if the doc didn't make it clear - the &quot;attesting&quot; that the doc
envisions isn't expected to be an API or anything in code - it's expected
to be something along the lines of a legal agreement or at least manual
verification and confirmation by the owners (process - whatever legal and
privacy think would be appropriate for the few dozen companies it would
apply to).&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

